Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.35\fay0.1\frz34\fs27\pos(1096,472)\c&HFFFFF1&}Mum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, mum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out? Where to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I like staying in my room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many people and too many cars are outside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have a good time alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Go out, … I will. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1a&H20H\fs108\fscx85\fad(640,0)\move(960,940,960,960,0,1200)\t(\fs120)}I Am Your\NTF Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:01:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I bump your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}It's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Shall I ask for a doctor on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}I'm really sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried if something goes wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}That's a nice guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you play guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my seat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you two take the train for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I? I'm on a trip
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A trip? It's called "a journey"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}I? Roaming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roaming? What's your destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Poetry and the soul afar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:53.38,Interp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}A quote from GAO Xiao-song (高晓松).
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zhong er{\i0} [delusive]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.14,Interp,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}"Zhong er bing"(中二病, ちゅうにびょう): hebephrenia, or adolescent delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}As a man in anime shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}who's more {\i1}zhong er{\i0} [delusive]?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids. Do you have OPPO?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My phone's out of charge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}May I borrow your VOOC Flash Charger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 5 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kids"? Who's a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}I'm taller than him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}I'm now fifteen, but have to be called a "kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence. I'm also fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, kids
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sixteen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are reading the same anime as me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you said it's {\i1}zhong er{\i0} [delusive]?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm YI Yang-qian-xi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm WANG Yuan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, {\i1}zhong er bing{\i0} [delusion]?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm WANG Jun-kai, roamer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Isn't here a famous resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get off here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to rob. Where's your money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}My wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your wallet on the train. Are you really sixteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the first time you are out alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}WANG Yuan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}WANG Jun-kai said he'll treat us for dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I treat you two for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}I'll search if there's something tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}There's a Chicken House nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fried chicken is my favourite
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,WANG Yuan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me to play the music
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}My fingers are greasy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Qian-xi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}It's out of charge. Can I charge it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep ocean, my hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about a running race here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who's the fastest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Start
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiya, run
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live the youth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall we go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting darker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Clover Forest near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}The fireflies there are quite famous
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}The scenery was on Hot Weibo Chart these days
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How about taking a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything good about fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just glowing bees
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:43.82,Interp,,0,0,0,,{\an2\b1\fs21\shad0.5\4a&H80H\pos(1436,80)\c&H5BFB0F&}Search
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Firefly, belongs to the order Coleoptera
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}is an insect which produces bioluminescence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Terrestrial fireflies generally inhabit places elusive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}lushly forested, and highly humid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Aquatic Fireflies requires stricter environment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}with no water pollution and light pollution
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Aiya, in short, it requires lush vegetation and plentiful water
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}But, fireflies appeared in Clover Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the photos on the web are beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Let's go and take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}WANG Jun-kai, you are expecting, too. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}All right. Now that you are longing, it's fine for me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just "fine"? You must
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.22,Interp,,0,0,0,,{\an2\b1\fs21\fad(360,0)\move(988,500,884,336,1000,1280)\t(1000,1280,\fs36)\c&HEBFFFF&}Traffic Accident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An accident happened in the tunnel. The road is closed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be possible? Everything went well on our way here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}We still have time if we go back now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to stay on this mountain overnight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Maybe we should go back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}Since you said fireflies are just glowing bees
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\bord0.1\3a&H80H}I hate giving up halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave if you want
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get there on my own
